snippet.title: Lemmings '95 gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Lemmings '95, PC game produced by Psygnosis in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/lemmings-95/5251/
Playing the Windows port of the classic Dos puzzle game. The game is identical.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.
